// go.work ties the root qurl module and the awsstore submodule together for
// local development so awsstore builds against the in-tree parent instead of a
// published tag. The root qurl module's go.mod stays free of the AWS SDK: the
// workspace only affects builds run from this tree, never what `go mod tidy`
// records in ./go.mod. Delete or ignore this file to build each module against
// its published dependencies.
go 1.26.4

use (
	.
	./awsstore
)
